text: Pirkko Pyykönen (born 18 June 1936) is a Finnish gymnast. She competed in seven events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Finland Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Helsinki
